         <abstract id="aspace_01fdb5593e6eae2610a5e877c0bb104a">This collection is comprised of peace rally handouts, newsclippings, related third party materials, and correspondence of the New Haven Peace Coalition, a local grass-roots effort, begun to protest the Gulf War, 1990-1991, and later the Second Gulf War and related conflicts.  Also included are materials related to the Connecticut Peace Coalition, a broader effort of the New Haven Peace Coalition, and the national Iraq Pledge of Resistance, 2003.</abstract>
